title: Skylighter's Turbo Pyro
description:
Skylighter's Turbo Pyro
-----------------------

Ever wanted to become a pyrotechnician? Or simply just make your own fireworks at home?

This book will take you through the basics, and get you started with 11 easy fireworks you can make in a weekend.


Remember: Doing any of the things in this book, is illegal in most countries!
A few countries will even send you to Guantanamo for it.
Check your local laws, and assess the risk before you get started :)


/Ubehage
